divs: Sighting DetailsHello, when me and my friend got home, my friend said he saw a plane, i live in one of the highest points in madison county, i looked at the plane and then i saw a star-looking object flying in a strait flight path over my house. In the past 13 years iv'e lived here, military planes and helicopters flue over my house, such as the following. C-5, MV-22 ospreys, a-10 thunderbolts, f-16, C-130, blackhawk helicopters, and a boieng 747. I saw a similar object a few months ago in the summer the same time, and my same friend was over. it does not make a noise, and it dissapeard in the clouds. And griffuss airforce base is fairly close to me in rome. Please email me back. Thank you.
